b'[Sacred Texts](../../index.htm)  [Hinduism](../index.htm)  [Index](index.htm)  \n[English](../gita/bg02.htm)  \n[Previous](bgs01.htm)  [Next](bgs03.htm)\n\n* * *\n\nII. atha dvit\xc4\xabyodhy\xc4\x81ya\xe1\xb8\xa5. (s\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x85khyayoga\xe1\xb8\xa5)  \n  \nsa\xc3\xb1jaya uv\xc4\x81ca  \n  \nta\xe1\xb9\x83 tath\xc4\x81 k\xe1\xb9\x9bpay\xc4\x81vi\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xadam a\xc5\x9brup\xc5\xabr\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81kulek\xe1\xb9\xa3a\xe1\xb9\x87am  \nvi\xe1\xb9\xa3\xc4\xabdantam ida\xe1\xb9\x83 v\xc4\x81kyam uv\xc4\x81ca madhus\xc5\xabdana\xe1\xb8\xa5 2.1  \n  \n\xc5\x9br\xc4\xabbhagav\xc4\x81n uv\xc4\x81ca  \n  \nkutas tv\xc4\x81 ka\xc5\x9bmalam ida\xe1\xb9\x83 vi\xe1\xb9\xa3ame samupasthitam  \nan\xc4\x81ryaju\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xadam asvargyam ak\xc4\xabrtikaram arjuna 2.2  \n  \nklaibya\xe1\xb9\x83 m\xc4\x81 sma gama\xe1\xb8\xa5 p\xc4\x81rtha naitat tvayy  \nupapadyate  \nk\xe1\xb9\xa3udra\xe1\xb9\x83 h\xe1\xb9\x9bdayadaurbalya\xe1\xb9\x83 tyaktvotti\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xadha para\xe1\xb9\x83tapa  \n2.3  \n  \narjuna uv\xc4\x81ca  \n  \nkatha\xe1\xb9\x83 bh\xc4\xab\xe1\xb9\xa3mam aha\xe1\xb9\x83 s\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x85khye dro\xe1\xb9\x87a\xe1\xb9\x83 ca  \nmadhus\xc5\xabdana  \ni\xe1\xb9\xa3ubhi\xe1\xb8\xa5 pratiyotsy\xc4\x81mi p\xc5\xabj\xc4\x81rh\xc4\x81v aris\xc5\xabdana 2.4  \n  \ngur\xc5\xabn ahatv\xc4\x81 hi mah\xc4\x81nubh\xc4\x81v\xc4\x81n  \n\xc5\x9breyo bhoktu\xe1\xb9\x83 bhaik\xe1\xb9\xa3yam ap\xc4\xabha loke  \nhatv\xc4\x81rthak\xc4\x81m\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83stu gurunihaiva  \nbhu\xc3\xb1jj\xc4\xabya bhog\xc4\x81n rudhirapradigdh\xc4\x81n 2.5  \n  \nna caitad vidma\xe1\xb8\xa5 kataran no gar\xc4\xabyo  \nyad v\xc4\x81 jayema yadi v\xc4\x81 no jayeyu\xe1\xb8\xa5  \ny\xc4\x81n eva hatv\xc4\x81 na jij\xc4\xabvi\xe1\xb9\xa3\xc4\x81mas  \ntevasthit\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 pramukhe dh\xc4\x81rtar\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xadr\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 2.6  \n  \nk\xc4\x81rpa\xe1\xb9\x87yado\xe1\xb9\xa3opahatasvabh\xc4\x81va\xe1\xb8\xa5  \np\xe1\xb9\x9bcch\xc4